<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Arman Kaınazarov</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
.G                   Am
 Bir shyndyq bar álemde,
.G               C
 Izdeseń sen tabarsyń.
.G               Am
 Iemdenseń egerde,
.G              C
 Ózińe jol asharsyń.

[C1]
   Qýanyshta toly Onda,
   Saǵan aıtamyn dostym!
   Qudaıǵa qurmet kórset,
   Óıtkeni Ol - mahabbat!

[V2]
 Qudaıǵa úmit artsań,
 Armanyń oryndalar!
 Sonda seniń boıyńda,
 Mahabbat oty janar!

[V3]
 Tabıǵatqa qarasam,
 Qudiretti kóremin!
 Qudaıdy madaqtasam,
 Júregimdi beremin!

[V4]
 Qudaıdyń balalary,
 Qýanyp án salyńdar.
 Kóktegi máńgilikte,
 Syıymyz sonda bolar!</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>Bir shyndyq bar álemde</title>
</song>